oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bilbrey Brothers Hardware Company
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the exterior of Bilbrey Brothers Hardware Company, once located at 305 North Main Street in Crossville. Shows two unidentified men standing in front of the store. There is also a rack of "Union" brand tools in front of the store, on right.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Stores & shops; Automobiles; People
